{"tid":1729153,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"1428 暴徒開咪警告或會開實彈！！！！！！！！！！！","createTime":"2019-11-17T06:31:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T07:59:02.000Z","uid":810,"like":90,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":89,"replies":[{"pid":"28b3f1fba7a5b6886821d59262f6cef7d447df8c","tid":1729153,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T06:31:31.000Z","msg":"六四來了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abf9e6dd79deea7f59734dad83859fa00492e5b8","tid":1729153,"uid":116054,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T06:31:57.000Z","msg":"救理大"},{"pid":"28a51aede984840208fd13fbf6ef72f3b75c35d6","tid":1729153,"uid":297230,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T06:32:03.000Z","msg":"他們在打的是「<strong>中共政權保衛戰</strong>」，而你們僅僅是在打「<strong>香港生活方式保衛戰</strong>」<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1728140/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1728140/page/1</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>（一） Be Water(水聚散) 不能變為Be Castle（碉堡戰、陣地戰）</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">對付Be Water，第一就是分化，把勇武派、和理非派拆分，第二步是下餌，引誘勇武派進入「必守的陣地」，刺激他們建立碉堡，最好所有的勇武派都集中進入少數陣地（例如四所大學），然後隔絕、撒網、一舉成擒。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>（二） 從「誰才是暴徒」辯論陷阱脫身</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">港人對抗港府還算旗鼓相當，畢竟兩邊都是被法治洗禮過的香港人，但是港人對付中共的無底綫宣傳統戰技能，坦白說，還是太嫩。世人關心香港事態的焦點從「港人要自由、要自治」，變成「人民和政府誰才是暴力方」的辯論，這正是北京要製造的焦點轉移。</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">（三） 一切回歸三個字 &ndash; 真普選</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">核心訴求只有一個：真普選，一切口號、行動、宣傳，都環繞真普選這單一訴求展開，這樣，世界聽得懂，連中國內地人民都聽得懂。</span>"},{"pid":"829eba566cb89df82072c08382149e6abd023ccc","tid":1729153,"uid":130797,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T06:32:05.000Z","msg":"去邊都好<br />\n快手開花<br />\n就算救唔到埋大手足<br />\n都要班狗承受損傷<br />\n狗屋狗宿呢d佢地承受唔起<br />\n堵路盡做啦<br />\n最緊要打到佢地老婆仔女個度先會識後悔<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"619de5e75d21eeeecad1332ffb9e7147aeabb3fa","tid":1729153,"uid":34047,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T06:32:31.000Z","msg":"仆街黑警"},{"pid":"f14c9c1e9e086d2eb75b5fb836b10e4b6c37f267","tid":1729153,"uid":7740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T06:32:31.000Z","msg":"Dllm la 實你老母"},{"pid":"0028967e350682875a765ca005a4b855e1b3f574","tid":1729153,"uid":105931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T06:32:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf28ffe078f77467bd53bcfc8a651d7e081c0680","tid":1729153,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T06:32:46.000Z","msg":"警：大學暴徒立即離開；五毛：立即散水；林奠建制：止暴成功，票投建制<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1728900\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1728900</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e0a8351eba2ce1c7f92f78f5dfa5fae5a32e0370","tid":1729153,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T06:32:49.000Z","msg":"六四來了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9817122f1fac3d75b989831bc895997faa1ece3","tid":1729153,"uid":53278,"like":2,"dislike":16,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T06:32:55.000Z","msg":"恨到啦你地<br />\n死守呀嘛"},{"pid":"dad9de38b3b7f47f71aa61bcbf01244d58d10fd8","tid":1729153,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T06:33:02.000Z","msg":"8964"},{"pid":"56d778